# --- Composite Helpers ---

@fn enc_load_imm64
@sig (rd: i64, val: i64) -> [i64]
@source_file src/codegen/arm64.aria
@source_line 410
@purpose Loads an arbitrary 64-bit immediate into a register using the minimum number of instructions: MOVZ for values 0..65535, MOVN for values -1..-65536, or MOVZ + up to 3 MOVK for larger values.
@post Returns 1-4 instruction words (plus sentinel at index 0).
@notes Optimizes common cases: small positives need 1 instruction, small negatives need 1 instruction. Worst case (all four 16-bit chunks non-zero) needs 4 instructions.

